1.en: Fearsome monsters give chase through a series of mazes as Conan, armed with his sword, battles them. Various levels allow you to play this adventure game with skills ranging from novice to professional. See how many monsters you can get.

2.en: Cosmic Raiders is a action game developed by Bally and was released for Bally Astrocade in 1981.
